        </speech>
        <speech by="#41fa6a70-397a-4597-900b-20b957bef948">
          <from>MR. GLAVINE</from>
          <p>MR. GLAVINE : Mr. Speaker, I'm sure those who are on long wait lists today are happy about $3 million going down to Cornwallis. I think you'll see something very different.</p>
