          <from>MS. DIANA WHALEN</from>
          <p>MS. DIANA WHALEN : Mr. Speaker, the previous Minister of Finance promised a balanced budget in the Spring on numerous occasions. He has now left the new Minister of Finance holding the bag, yet from day one in her new job the current Minister of Finance has been backing away from that commitment and tentative in her discussions of it. We're heading now to yet another broken promise.</p>
