          <from>MS. MAUREEN MACDONALD</from>
          <p>MS. MAUREEN MACDONALD : Mr. Speaker, the honourable member knows full well that this government did not cut $100 million from universities, for example. We did not cut the amounts of money that they say we cut - $65 million from education. It's a ridiculous allegation.</p>
